# Per-assignment ignores (large generated data, outputs) live in 1/.gitignore

# The paper source is on the `paper` branch; switching back to main leaves its build
# artifacts behind as untracked noise. Ignore the artifacts, not the directory — a bare
# `paper/` here would also ignore new .tex files if this ever merges into that branch.
paper/*.aux
paper/*.blg
paper/*.log
paper/*.out
paper/*.pdf
paper/*.toc
